the nuclearpowered carrier was built in more than 150 huge 
modular sections at newport news shipbuilding and dry dock co the 
only shipyard in the nation capable of building the 
1092footlong 91487ton vessels 
president bush today praised the thousands of workers who helped 
build the carrier and said it represents americas commitment to 
liberty 
bush called aircraft carriers an indispensable element of our 
