kuzmickas had a short and concrete conversation with gorbachev 
on friday after a joint meeting of the presidential and federation 
councils to discuss economic reform and a new treaty between moscow 
and the soviet republics 
she said both sides expressed the desire to start 
negotiations and strive for a convergence of positions in order to 
sign an agreement 
